♪I've wandered in the world♪

802
00:42:09,050 --> 00:42:12,050
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

803
00:42:13,610 --> 00:42:16,880
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

804
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:20,890
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

805
00:42:21,590 --> 00:42:23,520
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

806
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:28,980
♪How could I ever forget♪

807
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:31,840
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

808
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:34,360
♪To spend time with you♪

809
00:42:34,610 --> 00:42:35,970
♪When we grow old♪

810
00:42:35,970 --> 00:42:38,560
♪Nothing will change♪

811
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:40,160
♪The misty rains never cease♪

